{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDg4NjM1OTM3", "number": 3668, "title": "Change Netty logging level to INFO by default", "bodyText": "Signed-off-by: Lukas Kral lukywill16@gmail.com\nType of change\n\nEnhancement\n\nDescription\nIn our tests we can see that in CO log sometimes appear some \"errors\" and \"exceptions\" that are not really the errors and exceptions which we should take a care about -> that's because the logging level of netty is set by default to DEBUG. This PR gonna add to all 050-ConfigMap-strimzi-cluster-operator.yaml setting for the Netty logging level.\nChecklist\n\n Make sure all tests pass", "createdAt": "2020-09-17T12:34:21Z", "url": "https://github.com/strimzi/strimzi-kafka-operator/pull/3668", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "04d463f5dce8860db1a1dba99d3ab7e9974eaab0"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-09-20T14:49:15Z", "author": {"login": "im-konge"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 10, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdJwL-ygH2gAyNDg4NjM1OTM3OjE1MjdhYjZhM2U1NjQzMGVlYzZhYzQ5Y2VlZGNmNjcxZjA1YTcxMzY=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdKGOZZAFqTQ5MTUwMjY3NQ==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "1527ab6a3e56430eec6ac49ceedcf671f05a7136", "author": {"user": {"login": "im-konge", "name": "Luk\u00e1\u0161 Kr\u00e1l"}}, "url": "https://github.com/strimzi/strimzi-kafka-operator/commit/1527ab6a3e56430eec6ac49ceedcf671f05a7136", "committedDate": "2020-09-17T12:31:05Z", "message": "add netty logging to INFO\n\nSigned-off-by: Lukas Kral <lukywill16@gmail.com>"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NDkwNTU1Mjc4", "url": "https://github.com/strimzi/strimzi-kafka-operator/pull/3668#pullrequestreview-490555278", "createdAt": "2020-09-17T12:48:14Z", "commit": {"oid": "1527ab6a3e56430eec6ac49ceedcf671f05a7136"}, "state": "COMMENTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 1, "pageInfo": {"startCurs